column3: Nice trade places play on a free kick (wide midfielder slowly moves toward middle and someone else pops out wide at the last second before the kick to receive a pass)

One of the 6 midfielders (#6) is always taking looks as the ball is approaching
Outside mids are pinching way in and there is often very little width
column4: they are mainly unsuccessfully playing balls to space in the wide areas for players to run onto
